### Variables
@baseUrl = https://YOUR_PROJECT_REF.supabase.co/functions/v1
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Test 1 - Créer un devis complet (cas nominal)
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes/create-quote
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": "event-uuid-here",
  "items": [
    {
      "event_service_id": "event-service-uuid-1",
      "description": "Service traiteur premium",
      "quantity": 1,
      "unit_price": 2000000
    },
    {
      "event_service_id": "event-service-uuid-2",
      "description": "Décoration florale",
      "quantity": 1,
      "unit_price": 1500000
    }
  ],
  "tax_rate": 0.18,
  "discount_amount": 100000,
  "validity_date": "2024-12-31T23:59:59Z"
}

### Test 2 - Créer un devis avec items personnalisés
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes/create-quote
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": "event-uuid-here",
  "items": [
    {
      "description": "Service personnalisé",
      "quantity": 2,
      "unit_price": 500000
    }
  ]
}

### Test 3 - Erreur: event_id manquant
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes/create-quote
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    {
      "description": "Service",
      "quantity": 1,
      "unit_price": 1000000
    }
  ]
}

### Test 4 - Erreur: items vides
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes/create-quote
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": "event-uuid-here",
  "items": []
}

### Test 5 - Erreur: remise supérieure au sous-total
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes/create-quote
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": "event-uuid-here",
  "items": [
    {
      "description": "Service",
      "quantity": 1,
      "unit_price": 1000000
    }
  ],
  "discount_amount": 2000000
}

